/movies/news/rakhi-sawant-will-soon-be-seen-in-a-bhojpuri-item-song/articleshow/68083037.cms]</ref>\n|-\n| 2019 ||''[[Article 370 (film)|Article 370]]'' || || ||<ref>[https://www.glamsham.com/en/rakhi-sawant-to-shoot-an-item-number-for-article-370]</ref>\n|}\n\n==Music videos==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Song\n! Album\n! Language\n! Notes \n|-\n| 2003 || Jhoomka Gira Re Remix Sweet Honey Mix  ||  D.J. Hot Remix \u2013 Vol 3 || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2005 || \"Pardesiya Yeh Sach Hai Piya Remix\" ||  D.J. Hot Remix \u2013 Vol 3 || Hindi || \n|-\n| 2006 || \"Kajra Nite Remix\" || Kajra Nite Remix || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2007 || \"Haadsa\" || Universal Music || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2008 || \"Tu Dissda\" || Club Mix ||  Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2009 || \"Bhoot\" || Ishq Bector  ||  Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2010 || \"Jhagde\" || Ishq Bector || Hindi ||\n|-\n| 2019 || \"Chappan Churi\" || || Hindi ||<ref>[https://www.mid-day.com/articles/photos-rakhi-sawant-shoots-for-item-number-chappan-churi/21186186]</ref>\n|}\n\n==Television==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Title !! Network !!  Notes\n|-\n| 2006\n|''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 1)|Bigg Boss 1]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Sony Entertainment Television (India)|Sony TV]]\n| Contestant\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2007\n| ''Comedy Ka Badsshah \u2014 Hasega India''\n| Judge alongside [[Raju Srivastav]]\n|-\n| ''[[Nach Baliye 3]]''\n| [[Star Plus]]\n| Participant with [[Abhishek Avasthi]] ('''Runner-up''')\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2008\n|''Yeh Hai Jalwa''\n| [[9X (TV channel)|9X]]\n| Contestant ('''Winner''' with her team 'Chiller party')\n|-\n| ''The Rakhi Sawant Showz''\n| [[Zoom (Indian TV channel)|Zoom TV]]\n| Host\n|-\n| ''[[Chota Packet Bada Dhamaka]]''\n| [[Zee TV]]\n| Judge\n|-\n|''[[Jalwa Four 2 Ka 1]]''\n|9X\n|Contestant\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2009\n| ''[[Arre Deewano Mujhe Pehchano]]''\n| Star Plus\n| Contestant\n|-\n| ''[[Rakhi Ka Swayamwar]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[I