um]]\n|[[Sportpaleis]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|-\n|8 February 2021\n|[[Paris]]\n|[[France]]\n|[[AccorHotels Arena]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|-\n|10 February 2021\n|[[Milan]]\n|[[Italy]]\n|[[Mediolanum Forum]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|-\n|14 February 2021\n|[[Barcelona]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Spain]]\n|[[Palau Sant Jordi]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|-\n|16 February 2021\n|[[Madrid]]\n|[[Palacio de Deportes de la Comunidad de Madrid|WiZink Center]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" |Total\n!\u2014\n!\u2014\n|}\n\n===Cancelled shows===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+List of cancelled concerts\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:11em;\"|Date\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:11em;\"|City\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:9em;\"|Country\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:14em;\"|Venue\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10em;\"|Reason\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:5em;\" class=\"unsortable\" |{{Abbr|Ref(s)|References}}\n|-\n|10 May 2020\n|[[Copenhagen]]\n|[[Denmark]]\n|[[Royal Arena]]\n| rowspan=\"5\" |[[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic|Coronavirus pandemic]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" |<ref name=\"livenation\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.livenation.co.uk/artist/dua-lipa-tickets|title=Dua Lipa Tickets|last=|first=|date=24 March 2020|website=[[Live Nation]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324104559/https://www.livenation.co.uk/artist/dua-lipa-tickets|archive-date=24 March 2020|access-date=24 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|12 May 2020\n|[[Stockholm]]\n|[[Sweden]]\n|[[Ericsson Globe]]\n|-\n|13 May 2020\n|[[Oslo]]\n|[[Norway]]\n|[[Oslo Spektrum|Spektrum]]\n|-\n|22 May 2020{{efn|The 22 May 2020 show in Dundee, Scotland at Camperdown Country Park was due to be part of the 2020 [[Radio 1's Big Weekend]].<ref name=\"bigweekend\"/>|name=|group=}}\n|[[Dundee]]\n|Scotland\n|[[Camperdown Country Park]]\n|<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/newsbeat-51878354|title=Radio 1 Big Weekend cancelled due to coronavirus|date=13 March 2020|work=[[